AndStatus is a low traffic social networking client with tree-like threaded conversations. It supports multiple protocols, including [http://gnu.io/ GNU social] ([http://status.net/ StatusNet]), [http://twitter.com Twitter] and [http://pump.io Pump.io]. AndStatus combines your accounts from all networks into one Timeline and allows you reading and posting even while you are offline. 

For Android v.2.2+ devices. Open Source License.

For more information please read the [https://github.com/andstatus/andstatus/wiki AndStatus Wiki]. 
